name: Distant Harbors #1 - Sky Sanctuary
description: High up in the sky there is a sanctuary that creates lightning and thunder. It is built upon a fluffy cloud and is composed of high towers, hanging gardens and of course a lot of gears and pipes and all these things needed to kick up a fuss down here. Whilst most of the tech is placed externally, you will find a sanctuary of peace and tranquility inside. Welcome to the hallway!
